(1149, 33, 'right_side_text', '<h1>Thank you</h1>\r\n2016 has been groundbreaking for Hope and Homes for Children. And it is all down to you.\r\n\r\nThis year, thanks to your support, we have closed the badly named “Home of Hope” orphanage in Rwanda and found loving families for all 59 children who lived there. In Bosnia, 22 years after we rebuilt  the Bjelave orphanage in Sarajevo, we finally have the agreement to close the place, bringing full circle the work that Mark and Caroline Cook began there, back in 1994. At the beginning of this year, Ada, lived in Bjelave. Now, because of you, she has a real home and a family who love her. Your support has transformed her''s and many other children’s lives. Thank you.\r\n<p class="p1"><a class="button" href="http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/slide/donation-options-2/">Donate now</a></p>'),
