(5259, 349, 'right_side_text', '<h1><span style="color: #57244b;">Challenges </span></h1>\r\n<div class="col_main_small">\r\n<p class="intro_text">Whether you want to cycle through rural Africa or set a new personal best in the marathon, we have an adventure to suit you.</p>\r\n<p class="intro_text">Our team will be there to support you in everything from logistics and training tips to handy hints for fundraising. The hardest part will be deciding which challenge to undertake first!</p>\r\n<p class="intro_text">If you have your heart set on a particular challenge and you cannot find it in our listings <a href="mailto:community@hopeandhomes.org">get in touch</a> and we will do our best to turn your dream into reality.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a class="button" href="#">Call to action</a>'),
