(27, 1, '2016-11-03 09:55:42', '2016-11-03 09:55:42', 'Sign up to receive stories and updates from Hope and Homes for Children. They''re great. And we promise not share your details with anyone.\r\n\r\n[ninja_form id=2]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Be the first to know', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'join-newsletter', '', '', '2016-11-28 15:45:17', '2016-11-28 15:45:17', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=27', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
(28, 1, '2016-11-03 09:56:16', '2016-11-03 09:56:16', 'You are about to do something amazing. The money you donate will transform the lives of children around the world and bring us closer to a day where every child grows up in a loving, stable family. Thank you.', 'Donation options', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'donation-options', '', '', '2016-11-25 15:57:23', '2016-11-25 15:57:23', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=28', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
(29, 1, '2016-11-03 09:57:08', '2016-11-03 09:57:08', 'Hope and Homes for Children is at the forefront of a growing global movement to eradicate orphanages and these are exiting times for our organisation. Whether it''s news about orphanage closures, the success of our latest fundraising challenge or an update on our advocacy and work with other organisations around the world, you read the latest here:', 'The Latest', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-latest', '', '', '2016-12-02 13:28:20', '2016-12-02 13:28:20', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=29', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
(30, 1, '2016-11-03 10:01:57', '2016-11-03 10:01:57', 'We''re inspired by the courage and resilience of the children we work for. Read their stories here:', 'Stories', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stories', '', '', '2016-12-02 11:33:02', '2016-12-02 11:33:02', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=30', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
(31, 1, '2016-11-03 10:02:26', '2016-11-03 10:02:26', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHope and Homes for Children is working towards a day where every child can grow up in a loving family. We know we will only achieve this by working with others. Through our partnerships with national governments, civil society organisations, international agencies, corporate donors and committed individuals, we are helping to build a global movement that will eradicate orphanages in our lifetime.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'A global movement for change', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'global-reach-and-expertise', '', '', '2016-11-25 10:58:24', '2016-11-25 10:58:24', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=31', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
(32, 1, '2016-11-03 10:02:49', '2016-11-03 10:02:49', 'Every child wants a safe, loving family to grow up in. But over 8million children confined to orphanages around the world are being denied this, with often catastrophic effects.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'In numbers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'key-facts-to-quantify-issue', '', '', '2016-12-01 15:19:42', '2016-12-01 15:19:42', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=32', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
