(411, 1, '2016-12-02 11:55:44', '2016-12-02 11:55:44', '<strong>What we can offer you?</strong>\r\n\r\nHope and Homes for Children place a huge value on our philanthropic partnerships. We take time to get to know you and work alongside you to develop a long-term, mutually beneficial relationship, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>a dedicated account manager</li>\r\n 	<li>a range of funding options to suit your interests and objectives</li>\r\n 	<li>opportunities to meet our programmes teams and to see first hand the impact you are having</li>\r\n 	<li>a deep insight into our work through bespoke reports and updates</li>\r\n 	<li>substantial experience of grant management</li>\r\n 	<li>an exceptional level of service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Contact details</strong>\r\n<p class="p1">To discuss how you can play a key role in the global movement to eradicate orphanages please get in touch. We''d be delighted to talk to you.</p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><a href="mailto:pascale.costello@hopeandhomes.org">Pascale Costello</a></span>, Head of Grants Partnerships. <img class="alignnone wp-image-390" src="http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Phone-icon.png" alt="phone-icon" width="17" height="15" /> 01722 790111</p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><a href="mailto:sophie.wittenberg@hopeandhomes.org">Sophie Wittenberg</a></span>, Senior Major Partnerships Manager.<img class="alignnone wp-image-390" src="http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Phone-icon.png" alt="phone-icon" width="17" height="15" /> 0207 922 7907</p>', 'Philanthropy Detail', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'philanthropy-detail', '', '', '2016-12-02 11:56:57', '2016-12-02 11:56:57', '', 0, 'http://staging.webershandwicklondonstudio.co.uk/hhc/?post_type=slide&#038;p=411', 0, 'slide', '', 0),
